Interface EntryProcessorEvent

All Superinterfaces:
Event<EntryProcessorEvent.Type>, Event<EntryProcessorEvent.Type>, Iterable<BinaryEntry>
public interface EntryProcessorEvent extends Event<EntryProcessorEvent.Type>, Iterable<BinaryEntry>
An EntryProcessorEvent captures information relating to the execution of InvocableMap.EntryProcessors.
